    "details": {
      "biography": "<p>Summmoned by a @Compendium[wwn.abilities.gGSkuSIXyMEEp02Q]{Calculation of the Evoked Servitor} spell.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>The familiar always adopts the same shape for the same caster, though the initial casting can set this to any shape the caster wishes provided it&rsquo;s no larger than a small human. The familiar retains a telepathic connection with its creator and will obey any command it is given, including suicidal ones. It can perform any action that a competent human servant could. If the familiar is slain, it fades away, but can be called forth again by the spell. The familiar retains its memories of what happens while it&rsquo;s summoned, and can develop its own personality in time. The familiar remains in existence until dawn following the spell&rsquo;s casting or until dismissed by the caster.&nbsp;</p>\n</blockquote>",
